SMALL CRAFT WARNING: SOUTHEASTERLY WINDS WILL REACH FORCE 6 THIS MORNING
ON COASTS FROM MIZEN HEAD TO LOOP HEAD TO ERRIS HEAD EXTENDING TO ALL OTHER
